    "name": "马场模拟器 - Horse Farm Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3023600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i><strong>Horse Farm Simulator</strong></i> 是一款轻松的模拟游戏，让你可以建立并管理属于自己的马场，同时享受独特的骑马和农场生活体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><strong>马匹护理 🐴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >给你的马换马蹄铁，梳理它们的毛发，检查马鞍，定期喂食，不要让它们挨饿，保持干净以保护健康，并且别忘了清理马粪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/21cf22627b3d4a5e24d76f4fedce902c.poster.avif?t=1748251361\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/21cf22627b3d4a5e24d76f4fedce902c.webm?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/21cf22627b3d4a5e24d76f4fedce902c.mp4?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>农业 🥕</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的田地里种植各种作物，如胡萝卜、苜蓿和大麦，按时收获它们，并利用收成为你的马准备营养丰富的饲料，帮助它们保持健康和强壮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/e2d9a40096b622f9100a431d3df13492.poster.avif?t=1748251361\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/e2d9a40096b622f9100a431d3df13492.webm?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/e2d9a40096b622f9100a431d3df13492.mp4?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>咖啡馆管理 ☕</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你谦虚的咖啡馆里，为顾客准备并出售各种食物和饮料。利用这里赚取的收入生产更多产品，发展你的农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/3b868557eb256c9233ceb9618cc2dfa5.poster.avif?t=1748251361\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/3b868557eb256c9233ceb9618cc2dfa5.webm?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/3b868557eb256c9233ceb9618cc2dfa5.mp4?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>骑马与赛马 🏇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >累了吗？那就骑着你的马在镇上悠闲地骑行，或者参加一场马赛。如果你愿意，你还可以通过在赛马中下注来赚取奖金。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/497734a7ad1969a19afbbe3baaecdc38.poster.avif?t=1748251361\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/497734a7ad1969a19afbbe3baaecdc38.webm?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/497734a7ad1969a19afbbe3baaecdc38.mp4?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发展 ⏫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做出正确的投资来发展你的农场，添加新产品，并高效地利用资源。根据顾客需求增加咖啡馆或产品的种类，赚取收入，并利用这些收入发展你的农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/6b0a17b3f87b430b2abfc09da01840ee.poster.avif?t=1748251361\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/6b0a17b3f87b430b2abfc09da01840ee.webm?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023600/extras/6b0a17b3f87b430b2abfc09da01840ee.mp4?t=1748251361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入你梦想中的农场生活，尽在《<strong>Horse Farm Simulator</strong>》！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立你的农场，明智地管理你的生意，购买并定制你的马匹，在比赛中展示你的技能，满足顾客需求，发展你的农场。来吧，我们需要像你这样的农场主！</p>",
